name: SPURDO (SPURDO)
description: This is a historically top-tier super meme. It could be the new PEPE or Shiba Inu of this cycle, and it's no exaggeration to call it the return of the true king of memes. The community's goal is to make Spurdo a target for FOMO on the Ethereum chain and across all chains for years to come. SPURDO is a super meme that bridges Eastern and Western cultures. It has two sides: in the Chinese world, it's called "傻币" (Shă Bì), a meme even more extreme than Shiba Inu's Chinese name "屎币" (Shĭ Bì); in the Western world, it's a super meme that rivals Pepe.
